To the cook from Atlanta with the thin sauce- Cornstarch wasn't necessary. For peanut sauce, simply let the whole mixture simmer on the stove at about medium (keep stirring such that sugar on the bottom doesn't burn) for about 15 minutes and the sauce will approach the desired consistency. Hope that helps!

